# RNA Stability Benchmark â€“ GSE34204

This benchmark uses public RNA half-life measurements from GEO accession
GSE34204 (human lymphoblastoid cells).

## Dataset
- Source: Gene Expression Omnibus (GEO)
- Accession: GSE34204
- Measurement: mRNA half-life (hours)

## Benchmark Strategy
Transcripts are labeled as:
- Stable: top 25% longest half-lives
- Unstable: bottom 25% shortest half-lives

These labels are used to validate in silico oligo stability scoring rules.

## Disclaimer
Half-life is context-dependent and cell-type specific.
This benchmark is intended for relative comparison, not absolute prediction.
